          h4.subtitle 16 Week - Part Time
          p Web Development 100 is designed to teach beginners without any prior experience in web design or development how to build web applications. Spend the first 8 weeks of the course mastering the basics of front end programming, including HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The second half of the course takes a deeper dive into advanced front end web development.
          
